            name of persons who may exercise powers conferred by <ref>sections 19</ref> and
                <ref>20</ref> of the Ordinance</heading><content>The fee payable under <ref>section 21</ref> of the Ordinance for the designation by
            name of a person employed by the owner of an amusement ride who may exercise the powers
            conferred by <ref>sections 19</ref> and <ref>20</ref> of the Ordinance is $425 for each
            such person.</content><sourceNote>(<ref href="/hk/1996/ln60">L.N. 60 of 1996</ref>; <ref href="/hk/1997/ln29">L.N.
                29 of 1997</ref>; <ref href="/hk/1998/ln18">L.N. 18 of 1998</ref>; <ref href="/hk/1998/ln133">L.N. 133 of 1998</ref>; <ref href="/hk/2000/ln287">L.N. 287 of
