            (Safety) (Operation and Maintenance) Regulation</heading><subsection id="ID_1438412554298_004" name="1" temporalId="s5_1"><num value="1">(1)</num><leadIn>The fee payable under <ref>section 4</ref> of the Amusement Rides (Safety)
